---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Writings
---

<div class="page-intro">
    <h2>Writings</h2>
    <p>Articoli originali su marketing, media studies, content industries e management. Una collezione di pensieri su come gestire la complessità e costruire strategie che funzionano.</p>
</div>

{% for post in collections.writings %}
<article class="article-card">
    <div class="article-meta">
        <span class="article-date">{{ post.date | formatDate }}</span>
        {% if post.data.category %}
          {% if post.data.category.length %}
            {% for cat in post.data.category %}
            <span class="article-category">{{ cat }}</span>
            {% endfor %}
          {% else %}
          <span class="article-category">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
        {% if post.data.lang %}
        <span class="article-lang">{{ post.data.lang }}</span>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
    <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
    {% if post.data.description %}
    <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
    {% endif %}
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Continua a leggere →</a>
</article>
{% endfor %}